      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BE A BEAUTY (2) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 16.89 beating Aston Katy. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Can make it back-to-back wins. AUDACIOUS DODGE (1) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 0.8 lengths from the winner Brodie's Shadow in second(16.91) at this track. Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and two minor placings from three starts. Expected to be in this for a long way. GLAMOROUS GAL (8) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (16.99) at this track in a T3 RSTW. Lines up from box 8 for the first time. Bold showing expected. ONE KNEE NONI (5) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
